<div class="bg-perfil">
</div>
<div class="container profile">
  <div class="center-block">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
        <div class="image-container">
          <% if @user %>
            <% if @user.avatar %>
              <%= image_tag @user.avatar, size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
            <% else %>
              <%= image_tag "user.png", size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
            <% end %>
            <div class="progress">
              <% if @user.try(:profile) %>
                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= progress_bar(@user) %>%;" aria-valuenow="0" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">Importado <%= number_to_percentage(progress_bar(@user), precision: 0) %></div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="h4 text-center"><%= @user.try(:name) %></div>
            <div class="h6 text-center">
              <a href="https://github.com/<%= @user.try(:login) %>" title="<%= @user.try(:login) %>" target="_new">@<%= @user.try(:login) %></a>
            </div>
          <% else %>
            <%= image_tag "user.png", size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="evaluation-container">
          <% if @user.try(:profile).try(:evaluation) %>
            <% if asset_exists? "evaluation/#{@user.profile.try(:evaluation).try(:evaluation_type)}.png" %>
              <%= image_tag "evaluation/#{@user.profile.try(:evaluation).try(:evaluation_type)}.png", size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
            <% else %>
              <%= image_tag "evaluation/default.png", size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
            <% end %>
            <div class="progress">
              <% if @user.try(:profile) %>
                <div class="progress-bar bg-success progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= next_level_bar(@user)[:percentage] %>%;" aria-valuenow="0" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><%= next_level_bar(@user)[:number] %></div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="h4 text-center"><%= enum_i18n(Evaluation, "evaluation_type", @user.profile.try(:evaluation).try(:evaluation_type)) %></div>
            <div class="h6 text-center"><%= "#{@user.profile.try(:evaluation).try(:level)}º nível" %></div>
          <% else %>
            <%= image_tag "evaluation/default.png", size: "150x150", class: "profile-image" %>
            <div class="progress">
              <div class="progress-bar bg-success progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%;" aria-valuenow="0" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">?</div>
            </div>
            <div class="h4 text-center">?</div>
            <div class="h6 text-center">?º nível</div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% if @user.try(:profile) %>
      <% if progress_bar(@user) == 100 %>
        <% if @user == current_user %>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
              <%= link_to reimport_user_path(login: current_user.login), class: "btn btn-outline-info", method: :post do %>
                <i class="fab fa-github"></i> &nbsp; Reimportar
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <% if @user.try(:profile) %>
              <div class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">XP <%= @user.profile.score %></div>
            <% else %>
              <div class="btn btn-info btn-lg btn-block">?</div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-info">
            <span>
              A experiência é medida com base na quantidade de código criado. Não gostou? Leia a nota
              <a href="#nota">clique aqui</a>
            </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="h3">Projetos</div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="list-group">
                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start mb-2">
                      <small><%= image_tag "evaluation/started.png", size: "30x30" %></small>
                      <div class="h5 mb-1">Você tem
                        <strong><%= @user.repositories.where("commits_count < 50").count %></strong>
                        projeto(s)
                      </div>
                      <% if @user %>
                        <small class="text-muted">
                          com pouco código
                        </small>
                      <% else %>
                        <small class="text-muted">Você tem 0 projeto(s)</small>
                      <% end %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="list-group">
                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start mb-2">
                      <small><%= image_tag "evaluation/novice.png", size: "30x30" %></small>
                      <div class="h5" class="mb-1">Você
                        tem
                        <strong><%= @user.repositories.where("commits_count > 50 and commits_count < 100").count %></strong>
                        projeto(s)
                      </div>
                      <% if @user %>
                        <small class="text-muted">
                          com bastante código
                        </small>
                      <% else %>
                        <small class="text-muted">Você tem 0 projeto(s)</small>
                      <% end %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="list-group">
                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start mb-2">
                      <small><%= image_tag "evaluation/knight.png", size: "30x30" %></small>
                      <div class="h5" class="mb-1">Você tem
                        <strong><%= @user.repositories.where("commits_count > 100").count %></strong>
                        projeto(s)
                      </div>
                      <% if @user %>
                        <small class="text-muted">
                          com muito código.
                        </small>
                      <% else %>
                        <small class="text-muted">Você tem 0 projeto(s)</small>
                      <% end %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 ">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="h3">Linguagens</div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="h5"><%= image_tag "language/basic/default.png", size: "30x30" %>Básicas</div>
                  </div>
                  <ul class="list-group">
                    <% @user.profile.knowledges.where(knowledge_type: :basic).ordered_by_level.each do |knowledge| %>
                      <a class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                        <strong>
                          <% if asset_exists? "language/basic/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png" %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/basic/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% else %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/empty.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% end %>
                          <%= knowledge.language.description %>
                        </strong>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill"><%= knowledge.level %>º nível</span>
                        </div>
                      </a>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <div class="h5"><%= image_tag "language/normal/default.png", size: "30x30" %>Normais</div>
                  <ul class="list-group">
                    <% @user.profile.knowledges.where(knowledge_type: :normal).ordered_by_level.each do |knowledge| %>
                      <a class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                        <strong>
                          <% if asset_exists? "language/normal/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png" %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/normal/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% else %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/empty.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% end %>
                          <%= knowledge.language.description %>
                        </strong>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill"><%= knowledge.level %>º nível</span>
                        </div>
                      </a>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <div class="h5"><%= image_tag "language/rare/default.png", size: "30x30" %>Raras</div>
                  <ul class="list-group">
                    <% @user.profile.knowledges.where(knowledge_type: :rare).ordered_by_level.each do |knowledge| %>
                      <a class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                        <strong>
                          <% if asset_exists? "language/rare/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png" %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/rare/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% else %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/empty.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% end %>
                          <%= knowledge.language.description %>
                        </strong>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill"><%= knowledge.level %>º nível</span>
                        </div>
                      </a>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <div class="h5"><%= image_tag "language/special/default.png", size: "30x30" %>Especiais</div>
                  <ul class="list-group">
                    <% @user.profile.knowledges.where(knowledge_type: :special).ordered_by_level.each do |knowledge| %>
                      <a class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                        <strong>
                          <% if asset_exists? "language/special/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png" %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/special/#{knowledge.language.description.downcase}.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% else %>
                            <%= image_tag "language/empty.png", size: "30x30" %>
                          <% end %>
                          <%= knowledge.language.description %>
                        </strong>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill"><%= knowledge.level %>º nível</span>
                        </div>
                      </a>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
            <div class="h3">Seu XP é <%= @user.profile.score %>!</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <p class="alert-danger">O MERCADO DE TI ESTÁ MUDANDO. E BEM RÁPIDO!</p>
            <p>Acreditamos que você deveria se preparar para ele.</p>
            <p><%= link_to "Saiba Mais", new_interest_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
              <div id="nota" class="alert-info">NOTA</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <p>Ainda não levamos em consideração a Relevância e a Qualidade do código, somente a Quantidade. Nosso
                objetivo é disponibilizar na versão v1.1 e v1.2 respectivamente, hoje estamos na
                v0.3</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
              <%= link_to "Dúvidas, Críticas e Sugestões", new_contact_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>Precione F5 para acompanhar o processamento</h2>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    </div>
</div>
